1.0.10.name: wordpress/silver-spot
1.0.10.description: An elegant, electric silver-looking theme with excellent in-built SEO and an optional 'burnished' silver style that is reminiscent of tarnished white gold. It makes full use of the new theme customizer interface, giving you the option to change or remove header text and description as well as removing header widget.
